270
00:14:47,754 --> 00:14:49,594
- He may not have even
known what he was doing.

271
00:14:49,595 --> 00:14:51,857
I mean, spirits,
they can get confused.

272
00:14:51,858 --> 00:14:53,218
- Okay, then how do
we talk to him

