00:15:22,389 --> 00:15:23,619
you don't have all the facts,

287
00:15:23,623 --> 00:15:25,123
so maybe you don't need a spell.

288
00:15:25,125 --> 00:15:26,485
Maybe you need information,

289
00:15:26,493 --> 00:15:30,503
and Margo's Discipline
is gossip, so...

